      "body" : "<code>Math.toIntExact()</code> is good to know for Guava users. Guava <code>Ints.checkedCast</code> method&#39;s javadoc does not contain (unlike many other methods) warning for Java 8 users that there exists equivalent method built-in in core Java. It is usually useful information for those who strive for removing Guava from project where it has been brought before Java 8."
